Project: DBMigrator – C++ CLI-based DB Versioning Tool

Features:
    Versioned SQL migration scripts (001_init.sql, 002_add_users.sql, etc.)
    Applies only unapplied migrations
    Stores migration history in a special table
    Simple CLI: apply, status, reset


Project Structure

    DBMigrator/
    ├── CMakeLists.txt
    ├── main.cpp
    ├── db_migrator.cpp
    ├── db_migrator.h
    └── migrations/
        ├── 001_init.sql
        └── 002_add_users.sql
